  "text": "where u corresponds to the velocity field DOFs inside the elements,ū corresponds to the velocity DOFs on facets, and likewise for p andp. The HDG method in [CITATION_1] is such that element DOFs are local; a direct consequence is that A uu is a block diagonal matrix. Using this, we eliminate u from (4.2) and get the statically-condensed system",
